name: XMLElementPosition
shortdesc: Options for specifying position relative to the reference XML element or withing the XML element.

property.name: BEFORE_ELEMENT
property.shortdesc: Specifies the position before the XML element.

property.name: AFTER_ELEMENT
property.shortdesc: Specifies the position after the XML element.

property.name: ELEMENT_START
property.shortdesc: Specifies the position at the beginning of the XML element.

property.name: ELEMENT_END
property.shortdesc: Specifies the position at the end of the XML element.
